<item>
            <title>[LU-11572] tests: sanity-hsm test_260c is not reliable</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11572</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The test tries to check that RESTORE requests are not reordered when the coordinator is running its hottest code path (ie. not doing &apos;housekeeping&apos;).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The issue is that the test does not reliably make sure what code path the coordinator is running.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
